Source: https://github.com/nestjs/docs.nestjs.com/blob/master/content/techniques/performance.md

TypeScript code showing how to pass configuration options to the Fastify constructor through the FastifyAdapter. Example demonstrates enabling the logger option by passing an options object to the FastifyAdapter constructor.

```typescript
new FastifyAdapter({ logger: true });
```

