Source: https://github.com/nestjs/docs.nestjs.com/blob/master/content/security/helmet.md

Demonstrates how to import and register `@fastify/helmet` as a Fastify plugin using `app.register()` in a NestJS application. Unlike Express, it's used as a plugin, not a middleware.

```typescript
import helmet from '@fastify/helmet'
// somewhere in your initialization file
