### Configure Brotli Compression Quality in Fastify

Source: https://github.com/nestjs/docs.nestjs.com/blob/master/content/techniques/compression.md

This TypeScript example shows how to register the `@fastify/compress` plugin with custom Brotli options, specifically setting the compression quality to 4, which balances compression ratio and speed for Fastify applications. The quality can range from 0 (min) to 11 (max).

```typescript
import { constants } from 'node:zlib';
// somewhere in your initialization file
await app.register(compression, { brotliOptions: { params: { [constants.BROTLI_PARAM_QUALITY]: 4 } } });
```

