### Enable Raw Body Parsing in NestJS Fastify Application

Source: https://github.com/nestjs/docs.nestjs.com/blob/master/content/faq/raw-body.md

This snippet shows how to configure a NestJS application using Fastify to enable raw body parsing. By passing `rawBody: true` to the application options, the raw request body becomes available, which is essential for specific use cases like processing webhook payloads.

```typescript
import { NestFactory } from '@nestjs/core';
import {
  FastifyAdapter,
  NestFastifyApplication,
