### Configure CSP for NestJS with Fastify and Helmet

Source: https://github.com/nestjs/docs.nestjs.com/blob/master/content/openapi/introduction.md

This TypeScript code provides examples for configuring Content Security Policy (CSP) when using `fastify` and `helmet` with NestJS, specifically to avoid conflicts with Swagger UI. It shows how to define granular `directives` for various content sources or how to disable CSP entirely if not required for the application.

