```APIDOC
## FILE VALIDATION CONFIGURATION WITH BUILDER

### Description
Utilizing the `ParseFilePipeBuilder` to construct `ParseFilePipe` configurations with a cleaner, chained API. This simplifies adding multiple validators and setting pipe options.

